    "title": [
      "[Yasrenila, Wisteria Walk]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Lush curtains of wisteria drape from gnarled boughs that bend over the petal-strewn path leading through the trees.  Reflecting the moonlight breaking through the floral canopy, a fall of thirteen glass teardrops glints within the plethora of royal purple blooms.  Bats flit chaotically through the cloud-like shroud, diving toward the glittering droplets to pilfer a snack in the silver-cast forest.  A live-edge juniper bench nestles between a web of exposed roots."
    ],
